    </msub>
  </mrow>
</semantics></math>, respectively.</div></li></ul><div class='html-p'>The objectives for ensuring real-time security and threat detection in 6G CPS are:<div class='html-disp-formula-info' id='FD10-mathematics-13-01108'>
