gle Scholar</a>]</li><li id='B2-mathematics-13-01108' class='html-x' data-content='2.'>Blika, A.; Palmos, S.; Doukas, G.; Katsikas, S.K. Federated learning for enhanced cybersecurity and trustworthiness in 5g and 6g networks: A comprehensive survey. <span class='html-italic'>IEEE Open J. Commun. Soc.</span> <b>2024</b>, <span class='html-italic'>5</span>, 1234–1256. [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Federated+learning+for+enhanced+cybersecurity+and+trustworthiness+in+5g+and+6g+networks:+A+comprehensive+survey&author=Blika,+A.&author=Palmos,+S.&author=Doukas,+G.&author=Katsikas,+S.K.&publication_year=2024&journal=IEEE+Open+J.+Commun.+Soc.&volume=5&pages=1234%E2%80%931256&doi=10.1109/OJCOMS.2024.3449563" class='google-scholar' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>Google Scholar</a>] [<a href="https://doi.org/10.1109/OJCOMS.2024.3449563" class='cross-ref' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>CrossRef</a>]</li><li id='B3-mathematics-13-01108' class='html-x' data-content='3.'>Mohseni Ejiyeh, A. Real-time lightweight cloud-based access control for wearable iot devices: A zero trust protocol. In Proceedings of the First International Workshop on Security and Privacy of Sensing Systems, Istanbul, Turkey, 17 November 2023; pp. 22–29. [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Real-time+lightweight+cloud-based+access+control+for+wearable+iot+devices:+A+zero+trust+protocol&conference=Proceedings+of+the+First+International+Workshop+on+Security+and+Privacy+of+Sensing+Systems&author=Mohseni+Ejiyeh,+A.&publication_year=2023&pages=22%E2%80%9329" class='google-scholar' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>Google Scholar</a>]</li><li id='B4-mathematics-13-01108' class='html-x' data-content='4.'>Gil, S.; Yemini, M.; Chorti, A.; Nedić, A.; Poor, H.V.; Goldsmith, A.J. How physicality enables trust: A new era of trust-centered cyberphysical systems. <span class='html-italic'>arXiv</span> <b>2023</b>, arXiv:2301.12345. [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=How+physicality+enables+trust:+A+new+era+of+trust-centered+cyberphysical+systems&author=Gil,+S.&author=Yemini,+M.&author=Chorti,+A.&author=Nedi%C4%87,+A.&author=Poor,+H.V.&author=Goldsmith,+A.J.&publication_year=2023&journal=arXiv" class='google-scholar' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>Google Scholar</a>]</li><li id='B5-mathematics-13-01108' class='html-x' data-content='5.'>Hasan, K.M.B.; Sajid, M.; Lapina, M.A.; Shahid, M.; Kotecha, K. Blockchain technology meets 6g wireless networks: A systematic survey. <span class='html-italic'>Alex. Eng. J.</span> <b>2024</b>, <span class='html-italic'>92</span>, 199–220. [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Blockchain+technology+meets+6g+wireless+networks:+A+systematic+survey&author=Hasan,+K.M.B.&author=Sajid,+M.&author=Lapina,+M.A.&author=Shahid,+M.&author=Kotecha,+K.&publication_year=2024&journal=Alex.+Eng.+J.&volume=92&pages=199%E2%80%93220&doi=10.1016/j.aej.2024.02.031" class='google-scholar' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>Google Scholar</a>] [<a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.aej.2024.02.031" class='cross-ref' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>CrossRef</a>]</li><li id='B6-mathematics-13-01108' class='html-x' data-content='6.'>Liyanage, M.; Porambage, P.; Zeydan, E.; Senevirathne, T.; Siriwardhane, Y.; Yadav, A.K.; Siniarski, B. Advancing security for 6g smart networks and services. In Proceedings of the Joint European Conference on Networks and Communications &amp; 6G Summit (EuCNC/6G Summit), Antwerp, Belgium, 3–6 June 2024; pp. 616–621. [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Advancing+security+for+6g+smart+networks+and+services&conference=Proceedings+of+the+Joint+European+Conference+on+Networks+and+Communications+&+6G+Summit+(EuCNC/6G+Summit)&author=Liyanage,+M.&author=Porambage,+P.&author=Zeydan,+E.&author=Senevirathne,+T.&author=Siriwardhane,+Y.&author=Yadav,+A.K.&author=Siniarski,+B.&publication_year=2024&p