80%9394764" class='google-scholar' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>Google Scholar</a>]</li><li id='B10-mathematics-13-01108' class='html-xx' data-content='10.'>Nguyen, H.; Lim, Y.; Seo, M.; Jung, Y.; Kim, M.; Park, W. Strengthening information security through zero trust architecture: A case study in South Korea. In Proceedings of the International Conference on Intelligent Systems and Data Science, Can Tho, Vietnam, 11–12 November 2023; Springer: Singapore, 2023; pp. 63–77. [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Strengthening+information+security+through+zero+trust+architecture:+A+case+study+in+South+Korea&conference=Proceedings+of+the+International+Conference+on+Intelligent+Systems+and+Data+Science&author=Nguyen,+H.&author=Lim,+Y.&author=Seo,+M.&author=Jung,+Y.&author=Kim,+M.&author=Park,+W.&publication_year=2023&pages=63%E2%80%9377" class='google-scholar' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>Google Scholar</a>]</li><li id='B11-mathematics-13-01108' class='html-xx' data-content='11.'>Nie, S.; Ren, J.; Wu, R.; Han, P.; Han, Z.; Wan, W. Zero-trust access control mechanism based on blockchain and inner-product encryption in the internet of things in a 6g environment. <span class='html-italic'>Sensors</span> <b>2025</b>, <span class='html-italic'>25</span>, 123–135. [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Zero-trust+access+control+mechanism+based+on+blockchain+and+inner-product+encryption+in+the+internet+of+things+in+a+6g+environment&author=Nie,+S.&author=Ren,+J.&author=Wu,+R.&author=Han,+P.&author=Han,+Z.&author=Wan,+W.&publication_year=2025&journal=Sensors&volume=25&pages=123%E2%80%93135&doi=10.3390/s25020550&pmid=39860920" class='google-scholar' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>Google Scholar</a>] [<a href="https://doi.org/10.3390/s25020550" class='cross-ref' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>CrossRef</a>] [<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/39860920" class='cross-ref pub_med' data-typ='