                    <a href="mailto:?&amp;subject=From%20MDPI%3A%20%22Zero%20Trust%20Strategies%20for%20Cyber-Physical%20Systems%20in%206G%20Networks&quot;&amp;body=https://www.mdpi.com/3244564%3A%0A%0AZero%20Trust%20Strategies%20for%20Cyber-Physical%20Systems%20in%206G%20Networks

This%20study%20proposes%20a%20Zero%20Trust%20security%20framework%20for%206G-enabled%20Cyber-Physical%20Systems%20%28CPS%29%2C%20integrating%20Adaptive%20Access%20Control%20%28AAC%29%2C%20end-to-end%20encryption%2C%20and%20blockchain%20to%20enhance%20security%2C%20scalability%2C%20and%20real-time%20threat%20detection.%20As%206G%20networks%20facilitate%20massive%20device%20connectivity%20and%20low-latency%20communication%2C%20traditional%20perimeter-based%20security%20models%20are%20inadequate%20against%20evolving%20cyber%20threats%20such%20as%20Man-in-the-Middle%20%28MITM%29%20attacks%2C%20Distributed%20Denial-of-Service%20%28DDoS%29%2C%20and%20data%20breaches.%20Zero%20Trust%20security%20eliminates%20implicit%20trust%20by%20enforcing%20continuous%20authentication%2C%20strict%20access%20control%2C%20and%20real-time%20anomaly%20detection%20to%20mitigate%20potential%20threats%20dynamically.%20The%20proposed%20framework%20leverages%20blockchain%20technology%20to%20ensure%20tamper-proof%20data%20integrity%20and%20decentralized%20authentication%2C%20preventing%20unauthorized%20modifications%20to%20CPS%20data.%20Additionally%2C%20AI-driven%20anomaly%20detection%20identifies%20suspicious%20behavior%20in%20real%20time%2C%20optimizing%20security%20response%20mechanisms%20and%20reducing%20false%20positives.%20Experimental%20evaluations%20demonstrate%20a%2040%25%20reduction%20in%20MITM%20attack%20success%20rates%2C%205.8%25%20improvement%20in%20authentication%20efficiency%2C%20and%2063.5%25%20lower%20latency%20compared%20to%20traditional%20security%20methods.%20The%20framework%20also%20achieves%20high%20scalability%20and%20energy%20efficiency%2C%20maintaining%20consistent[...]" title="Email">
                        <i class="fa fa-envelope-square" style="font-size: 30px;"></i>
                    </a>

                                        <a href="https://x.com/intent/tweet?text=Zero+Trust+Strategies+for+Cyber-Physical+Systems+in+6G+Networks&amp;hashtags=mdpimathematics&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mdpi.com%2F3244564&amp;via=MathematicsMDPI" onclick="windowOpen(this.href,600,800); return false" title="Twitter" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
